[DhtmlXQ_comment27]And it would be an attacking game for both.||In summary:||Red's left side horse and pawn ranked chariot variation has shown to be statiscally inefficient in the past, and has not received the results that red would want, thereby leading to a decrease in its usage.||In the past few years however, many young players have studied and greatly enriched the content of this opening.||The variations shown here are all from actual games played.||From the looks of things, this opening would still have much room for study in the years to come.  　[/DhtmlXQ_comment27]
